{
  "info": {
    "name": "Microservices con Kafka",
    "description": "Colección Postman para probar el flujo completo: Cliente → Producto → Pedido → Kafka → Notificación\n\n## Puertos\n- Gateway: 8088 (host) → 8080 (container)\n- Eureka: 8761\n- customer-service: 8081\n- product-service: 8082\n- order-service: 8083\n- notification-service: 8084\n\n## Flujo de prueba (orden recomendado)\n1. Crear cliente\n2. Crear producto\n3. Crear pedido (usa clienteId y productoId de los pasos anteriores)\n4. Ver notificación en logs de notification-service\n5. Consultar/listar recursos\n6. Actualizar recursos\n7. Eliminar recursos",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Clientes",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear cliente",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('clienteId', jsonData.id);",
                  "    console.log('clienteId guardado:', jsonData.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Juan Pérez\",\n  \"correo\": \"juan@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clientes",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clientes"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar clientes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clientes?page=0&size=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clientes"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "10" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener cliente por ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clientes/{{clienteId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clientes", "{{clienteId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar cliente",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Juan Pérez Actualizado\",\n  \"correo\": \"juan.nuevo@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clientes/{{clienteId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clientes", "{{clienteId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar cliente",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clientes/{{clienteId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clientes", "{{clienteId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear cliente duplicado (error 409)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Juan Pérez\",\n  \"correo\": \"juan@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clientes",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clientes"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
